sellerCard.description: I am a skilled Full Stack Developer and Shopify expert with 6 Years of experience in building high-performing, visually appealing, and fully functional e-commerce websites. Whether you need a custom Shopify store, seamless app integrations, or backend functionality enhancements, I’ve got you covered! My expertise includes Shopify theme customization, API integrations, troubleshooting, and ensuring optimal performance for your online store. Let’s bring your e-commerce vision to life!

description.content:
Shopify, Shopify Website, Shopify Design


So, you're thinking about setting up your shopify website or dropshipping store? Awesome move! I specialize in making that process smooth as butter with my Shopify Store Development and Product Landing Page Gig.


Here's the scoop on what I bring to the table:


Why This Gig?


  • Shopify Store with Premium Professional design
  • Dropshipping Store
  • Responsive on all devices
  • Elegant and sleek design
  • Domain and SSL setup
  • Creation of information pages (Terms of Service, Shipping, etc)
  • GTM integration
  • Setup Payment Gateway
  • Free 14 days Support
  • And Many More




Sound like a plan? Let's team up and turn your online dreams into reality. Shoot me a message, and let's get this party started!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide hosting and domain?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, I don't provide hosting or domain. You need to purchase a shopify account and domain, however I can guide you the process.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide support after order completion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we do provide one month support even after the completion.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will website be responsive?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes website will be responsive on all devices.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can we do a video or audio call before starting the project.
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes we can do a video or audio call before starting to understand the requirements easily

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I also request a urgent delivery
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Hi,
Yes I do work on urgent deliveries as well. But please message me before to know my availablity

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide UI/UX service?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes I do provide UI and UX services so that you have better idea of design
